  <section>
    <h>uses</h>
    <section id="uses-root">
      <h>root</h>
      <p><g>an</g> can be used as the root of a direct question.</p>
      <p>cf. <a href="?gd=bi#a_bheil"><g>A bheil ... ?</g></a> <en>Is/are ... ?</en></p>
